---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Demo af Client Room — SitedokAI" description="Se en demo af SitedokAI Client Room og forstå hvad du får for 2.495 kr. PDF følger med som eksport.">
  <Nav />
  <main>

    <!-- Demo Header -->
    <section class="bg-brand border-b border-white/10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-20">
        <p class="text-sm text-accent-light font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Demo</p>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
          Nordisk Køkken
        </h1>
        <p class="text-white/50 text-lg mb-2">Eksempel på Client Room for AI-synlighed og website-sundhed</p>
        <p class="text-white/30 text-sm">Genereret 5. april 2026 &middot; SitedokAI</p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-white/40 border border-white/10 inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
          Fiktiv virksomhed — din leverance vil være tilpasset din virksomhed.
          <a href="/demo-rapport.html" class="text-accent-light underline ml-1 hover:text-white transition-colors">Se PDF-eksporten &rarr;</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Overall Score -->
    <section class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold mb-4">Samlet AI-synlighedsscore</p>
          <div class="inline-flex items-end gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="font-display text-7xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold text-score-red">32</span>
            <span class="text-2xl text-gray-300 font-bold mb-3">/100</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-block bg-red-50 text-score-red text-sm font-bold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
            Lav synlighed
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
            Nordisk Køkken er stort set usynlig for AI-søgemaskiner. Konkurrenter dominerer anbefalingerne.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Platform Breakdown -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-brand mb-6">Hvor virksomheden bliver valgt</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand">ChatGPT</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-score-red bg-red-50 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Ikke synlig</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Nævner ikke Nordisk Køkken ved relevante søgninger som "bedste restauranter København" og "dansk frokostordning".</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand">Google AI</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-score-red bg-red-50 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Konkurrent dominerer</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Viser konkurrent MadMarkedet i AI-svarene 3x oftere. Nordisk Køkken nævnes kun i forbindelse med anmeldelser fra 2022.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand">Codex</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-score-yellow bg-yellow-50 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Begrænset</span>
            </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Begrænset synlighed. Mangler tydelige sider og stærke tegn på troværdighed på tværs af platforme.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand">Gemini</h3>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-score-yellow bg-yellow-50 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Forældet info</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Finder virksomheden men med forældet information. Viser gammel adresse og udgået menukort. Opdateret indhold når ikke igennem.</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Technical Scores -->
    <section class="bg-white border-b border-gray-200">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-brand mb-6">Teknisk website audit</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-4xl font-extrabold text-score-green mb-1">78</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Performance</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-4xl font-extrabold text-score-green mb-1">92</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Sikkerhed</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-4xl font-extrabold text-score-yellow mb-1">61</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">SEO</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="font-display text-4xl font-extrabold text-score-yellow mb-1">55</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Core Web Vitals</p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Findings -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-brand mb-6">Vigtigste fund</h2>
        <div class="space-y-3">

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-score-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand text-sm mb-1">Ingen schema markup (JSON-LD)</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Hjemmesiden mangler strukturerede data helt. AI-modeller kan ikke identificere virksomhedstype, lokation, menukort eller åbningstider.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-red-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-score-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand text-sm mb-1">Konkurrenten MadMarkedet er 3x mere synlig</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">MadMarkedet nævnes konsekvent af ChatGPT og Google AI pga. aktiv blog, opdaterede Google Business-data og korrekt implementeret schema markup.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-score-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand text-sm mb-1">Core Web Vitals under grænsen</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">LCP på 4.2s (grænse: 2.5s) og CLS på 0.18 (grænse: 0.1). Langsom indlæsning og layout-skift påvirker både brugeroplevelse og AI-crawlere.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-score-yellow" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-brand text-sm mb-1">Forældet indhold spredt online</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Gemini og andre modeller trækker gammel information fra Yelp, TripAdvisor og uopdaterede kataloger. Aktiv opdatering af profiler anbefales.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
        <div class="bg-brand rounded-2xl p-10 md:p-14 text-center">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">
            Vil du se din egen kundeoplevelse?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/50 mb-8 max-w-lg mx-auto">
            Få en AI-audit tilpasset din virksomhed med Client Room, konkurrentbillede og næste skridt. Klar inden for 48 timer.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a href="/demo-rapport.html" class="inline-block bg-white text-brand px-8 py-3.5 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors rounded-md">
              Se PDF-eksporten
            </a>
            <a href="/#contact" class="inline-block border-2 border-white/20 text-white px-8 py-3.5 font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors rounded-md">
              Bestil din audit &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
